title: CNBC Daily Open: Amazon one-ups its rivals on capex spending, but investors are already worried over AI valuations
summary_full: Amazon's capital expenditure projection comes in at $200 billion, above analysts' estimates of $146.6 billion and higher than the roughly $131 billion in 2025.
